    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>A jar of this unguent is 3 inches in diameter and 1 inch deep, and contains 5 applications. Placed upon a poisoned wound or swallowed, the ointment detoxifies any poison (as neutralize poison with a +5 bonus on the check). Applied to a diseased area, it removes the disease (as remove disease with a +5 bonus on the check). Rubbed on a wound, the ointment cures 1d8+5 points of damage (as cure light wounds).<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item, cure light wounds, neutralize poison, remove disease</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Ultimate Equipment",
